<p>A one-second delay in page load time reduces conversions by 7%. For a blog generating 10,000 monthly visits, that delay costs hundreds of potential leads.</p>
<h3>The Visual Search Opportunity</h3>
<p>Visual search is not a future trend. It is a current traffic source. Google Lens, Pinterest Lens, and AI search features all pull from optimized images.</p>
