<h3>Pre-Upload Checklist</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Image format is WebP or AVIF (not raw JPEG or PNG)</li>
<li>[ ] File name is descriptive with hyphens between words</li>
<li>[ ] File name includes a relevant keyword naturally</li>
