<li>[ ] Responsive srcset defined for multiple sizes</li>
<li>[ ] Image CDN configured for global delivery</li>
<li>[ ] Browser caching headers set for 365+ days</li>
</ul>
<h3>Post-Publish Verification</h3>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Page passes Core Web Vitals assessment</li>
<li>[ ] LCP is under 2.5 seconds</li>
<li>[ ] CLS is under 0.1</li>
<li>[ ] Images appear in Google Search Console image report</li>
<li>[ ] No broken image links</li>
</ul>
